        type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "<b><u>Game Rules</u></b>\n\nMove to the start position to begin the
        countdown. \n\nGrab and pull the slingshot with either controller or hands,
        aim and release to hit the most targets first.\n\nThe player with the highest
        score before time runs out wins."
